# predict-genre
predict the genre of music. this was a microproject i had to do for my practical python classes in college.


# note
download the [gtzan dataset](https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/andradaolteanu/gtzan-dataset-music-genre-classification) and place it in `/src/data`


